Does everything the old version does PLUS MORE. The player can now pickup items just by walking over them. 
You can now wear an item by pressing w and pressing a number that corresponds to the carry slot.
You can now take of an item by pressing t and then pressing the number corresponds to the carry slot.
You can drop items by pressing d.
Expunges and item from the game by pressing the x and the corresponding carry slot number.
Pressing i opens pc inventory and pressing e opens equipped.
Pressing , inspects the item.